{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLFormElement.name","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/name","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>form の <code>name</code> 属性は、その <code>form</code> 要素の名前を文字列として返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>string</em> = form.name; //取得\nform.name = <em>string</em>; //設定</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> form1_Name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"form1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>form1_Name <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>form<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token comment\">// browser doesn't support this form of reference</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注意","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この属性は読み書きともに可能であり、フォーム名の読取り及び設定に使用できます。</p>\n<p>もしフォーム内に \"name\" と名付けられた要素を含めてしまった場合、その要素が優先され、<code>name</code> 属性でのフォームオーナーへのアクセスが出来なくなってしまいます。</p>\n<p>Internet Explorer (IE) では、<code>createElement()</code> メソッドによって作成された要素に対する <code>name</code> 属性を用いての名前の設定 / 書換は許可されていません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/forms.html#dom-form-name\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5, Section 4.10.3, The form Element</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-22051454\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 HTML: name</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"summary"},{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"注意","id":"notes"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"}],"summary":"form の name 属性は、その form 要素の名前を文字列として返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLFormElement.name","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.name","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.name","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/htmlformelement/name","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/htmlformelement/name/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement","title":"HTMLFormElement"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/name","title":"HTMLFormElement.name"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLFormElement.name - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}